Installing the dependencies:
----------------------------

$ bower install
$ pip install -r requirements.txt -t lib/

Workaround for RAND_egd import issue:
-------------------------------------

This may be needed if appengine dies with SSL due
to being unable to import RAND_egd.

See the patch:
https://issuetracker.google.com/issues/35900282

See the discussion:
https://issuetracker.google.com/issues/35899425
